3
00:00:41,720 --> 00:00:42,960
It's so humiliating!

4
00:00:42,960 --> 00:00:45,240
I can't face anyone again.

5
00:00:45,240 --> 00:00:46,240
Mankui,

6
00:00:46,240 --> 00:00:47,360
