10
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,760
I don't want it.

11
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:56,520
Except for Qilu,

12
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,760
I don't want anyone.

13
00:00:57,760 --> 00:00:58,200
OK, OK.

14
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:58,920
No one else.

15
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,560
I wonder what Han Qilu

16
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:03,640
