17
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:07,000
Hello?

18
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:10,840
You mean,

19
00:01:10,840 --> 00:01:12,200
Han Qilu did that

20
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:15,120
for a girl

21
00:01:15,120 --> 00:01:17,120
called An Chuxia?

22
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,120
She has been living with the Han family

23
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,560
and studying

24
00:01:20,560 --> 00:01:21,680
in Stilan College?

25
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:23,560
Isn't she Han Qilu's

26
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,120
personal assistant?

27
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:25,920
Assistant?

28
00:01:27,040 --> 00:01:28,960
Would an assistant
go to school with him

29
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:30,200
or live together with him?

30
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:39,600
Suspend the search for the girl.

31
00:01:39,600 --> 00:01:40,760
Help me find another girl first.

32
00:01:40,760 --> 00:01:41,560
Her name is An Chuxia,

33
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:42,680
the same age as me.

34
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,320
Her mom just had

35
00:01:43,320 --> 00:01:44,600
a kidney transplant.

36
00:01:45,400 --> 00:01:45,840
Yeah.

37
00:01:46,480 --> 00:01:47,040
Hurry up.

38
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,400
Qilu,

39
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,960
I'm disappointed in you.

40
00:01:55,760 --> 00:01:57,560
What can I do to satisfy you?

41
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,560
Get engaged to Xiang Mankui,

42
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,120
