50
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,840
Our families must unite by marriage.

51
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,440
Everyone has the right to say that

52
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:21,600
except you.

53
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:22,720
Back then,

54
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,640
